{% /table %}

---

### **In Summary**

> Search technologies form the *engine of discovery* on the web.\
They crawl, analyze, and rank the ocean of information —\
turning chaos into instant answers.

Every search result you see is the product of complex engineering, mathematics, and linguistic intelligence working behind the scenes.
